{"tid":1724157,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【航空台】澳航成功完成倫敦至悉尼歷史性直航","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:45:56.000Z","uid":120678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7a074d516e876499f357c07e9128da90cc77cf","tid":1724157,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=370049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370049&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=e1e2a756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370049&h=712a7dd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=370049</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dynaimage.cdn.cnn.com/cnn/q_auto,w_634,c_fill,g_auto,h_357,ar_16:9/http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cnn.com%2Fcnnnext%2Fdam%2Fassets%2F191115155459-qantas-test-flight-landing-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdynaimage.cdn.cnn.com%2Fcnn%2Fq_auto%2Cw_634%2Cc_fill%2Cg_auto%2Ch_357%2Car_16%3A9%2Fhttp%253A%252F%252Fcdn.cnn.com%252Fcnnnext%252Fdam%252Fassets%252F191115155459-qantas-test-flight-landing-2.jpg&h=09cea53b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲航空成功試驗全球最長途不停站飛行，由倫敦直飛悉尼，全程19小時19分鐘，下個月會再度試飛紐約至悉尼的直航航線。<br />\n<br />\n經過19小時19分鐘旅途，澳洲航空QF7879客機從英國倫敦不停站飛抵澳洲悉尼，比原定時間遲了45分鐘，不完美，但可接受。民眾在停機坪歡迎這架波音787-9夢幻客機圓夢歸航。<br />\n<br />\n機上載有52人，包括澳航行政總裁喬伊斯和四名機師。主機師表示，四名機師輪流駕駛，每人有兩節四小時的休息，飛得頗輕鬆。<br />\n<br />\n今次全球最長途不停站飛行，由倫敦直飛悉尼17800公里，歷時19小時19分鐘。上個月澳航另一場試飛紐約直達悉尼16200公里，花上19小時16分鐘，機上的燈光、餐飲和運動時間經過精心設計，乘客要戴着監察器，記錄褪黑激素等指標，了解長時間飛行對身心狀況的影響。<br />\n<br />\n超長途直飛航班由日出飛到日落再日出，因而名為「日出計劃」，下個月澳航再試飛紐約至悉尼的航線，年底決定是否營運，預計最快2022年開辦。"},{"pid":"4ddc2098b309665cb01dd088af61b504358bb700","tid":1724157,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"比2個300磅 肥佬夾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856fabc42b07d8b2c17b3b611cb4afe73fd49306","tid":1724157,"uid":335434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"呢個世界最遠嘅航程唔係流浮山去元朗咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752550776fc7f9a3648a1770f78384fcbe709666","tid":1724157,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ddc2098b309665cb01dd088af61b504358bb700","tid":1724157,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"比2個300磅 肥佬夾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:40:39.000Z","msg":"坐20粒鐘Econ真係唔敢博..寧願經中東或者新加坡轉機仲好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae7aeb1348401818e4d6a6203d30289b1412ddf","tid":1724157,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"20個鐘Econ會想死"}]}